EnvBoot
=======

Quickly set up working environments on new systems.

Software
--------

 * Adium (https://adium.im/)
 * Anaconda (https://store.continuum.io/cshop/anaconda/)
 * Modular Bash
 * Chromium (http://www.freesmug.org/chromium)
 * Condawrapper (https://github.com/adamlwgriffiths/condawrapper)
 * DropBox (https://dropbox.com)
 * Foreman (https://github.com/ddollar/foreman)
 * Git (http://www.git-scm.com/)
 * Heroku-toolbelt (https://toolbelt.heroku.com)
 * Homebrew (http://brew.sh/)
 * iTerm2 (http://iterm2.com/)
 * Ruby (https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/)
 * SublimeText2 (http://www.sublimetext.com/)
 * VirtualBox (https://www.virtualbox.org)


    # OS-X
    wget -q0- -O envboot.zip https://github.com/adamlwgriffiths/envboot/archive/master.zip && unzip envboot.zip && rm envboot.zip && cd envboot && ./osx.sh
    
    # Ubuntu
    wget -q0- -O envboot.zip https://github.com/adamlwgriffiths/envboot/archive/master.zip && unzip envboot.zip && rm envboot.zip && cd envboot && ./ubuntu.sh

